News.Title: Onyx Biotec: Weak Market Debut with 11.5% Discount on Listing
News.Summary: Onyx Biotec listed at ₹54 on NSE SME, 11.5% below its IPO price of ₹61. The stock recovered slightly post-listing to ₹56.75. The ₹29.34 crore IPO was oversubscribed 198 times. Proceeds will be used for manufacturing upgrades, loan repayment, and corporate purposes.
